geria yesterday said that Patrick Akinwuntan will take over from Charles Kie as its new Managing Director/Chief Executive. July 20, 2018 In "Business" The Vice Chancellor, University of Lagos, ProfessorOluwatoyin Ogundipe has commended Ecobank for its consistent support for the promotion of entrepreneurship among students and youths across the country September 6, 2019 In "News" The Managing Director of Ecobank Nigeria, Mr. Patrick Akinwuntan has announced that the bank has upgraded its core banking application being part of the bank’s commitment to ensuring customers receive the best service possible. November 29, 2018 In "News"